  <title>Changing the Scaling Factor</title>

  <media type="image" src="figures/scale.png">
    <p>Changing the scaling factor</p>
  </media>

  <p>
    You can scale the ruler's unit by a factor.
    When you define a scaling factor, a reminder is displayed on the ruler.
  </p>

  <steps>
    <item><p>Click the menu button (<media its:translate="no" type="image" src="figures/open-menu-symbolic.svg"/>) in the left-side corner of the ruler.</p></item>

    <item><p>Adjust the scaling factor.</p></item>
  </steps>

